data.description: Beautiful home in gated community of Rolling Hills Ranch with NO MELLO ROOS. Home features high ceilings with plenty of light,  tile and wood floors,  two fireplaces,  upstairs office with balcony an Expansive master bedroom with french doors that lead out to a private balcony, ensuite bath with large tub that include jets,  granite countertop and large closet with custom  organizer. Spacious kitchen with granite countertop, stainless steel appliances and large eat in island.   Family room features fireplace, custom built in cabinet, and custom built in shutters.  Downstairs bedroom with a large sitting area and private bath is perfect for guest.  Home sits on a large corner lot at the end of a private cul de sac.
